paper_abstract: CytoModeler is an open-source Java application based on the Cytoscape platform. It integrates large-scale network analysis and quantitative modeling by combining omics analysis on the Cytoscape platform, access to deterministic and stochastic simulators, and static and dynamic network context visualizations of simulation results.
paper_title: CytoModeler: a tool for bridging large-scale network analysis and dynamic quantitative modeling
